data.description: Seller offering $10,000 towards Buyer's Closing Expenses, plus upgraded one year home warranty, plus . Welcome to your happy place!  This charming home features all main living areas on the main floor with minimal steps going in.  The open concept means never being stuck in the kitchen and missing all the fun.  The primary bedroom is separated from the two extra bedrooms by living area for added privacy.  Located off the kitchen are stairs leading to the large bonus space with its own attached full bathroom.    Enjoy morning coffee on the  deck overlooking a wooded area instead of backyard neighbors.  Located in sought after Sango area of Clarksville with easy access to I24 for those trips to Kentucky Lake or Nashville!   Let me give you a tour of this home today.
